000Z","msg":"「現在泛民主派捧中共出來」<br />\n即係點 佢地做左乜<br />\n呢排無留意佢地<br />\n<br />\n到割定唔割, 都要predict一下割左之後利大於弊定弊大於利<br />\n如果唔係 唔割有何妨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T21:20:15.000Z","msg":"其實點解唔可以屌泛民？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528735\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528735</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭革命，最後關頭反對派與總統密會妥協，市民反對無視密會協議，推翻結果，總統逃逸。<br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉革命，最後關頭親美反對派與政府協商妥協，美國為首外部勢力見勢色不對，收回支援力量，革命至今仍在進行中。<br />\n<br />\n香港革命，最後關頭泛民主派發信習近平，要求中央重啟政改，無視美方港美關係法及人權民主法案進程，以中港內政追逐假雙普選，延誤英美外部監管之真雙普選。下午由林鄭月娥辦公室發信拆除泛民炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n割蓆後利大於弊。市民安心在美國協調下be water抗爭。"},{"pid":"ea098b6f591f2344827c8649b609d81a59afa871","tid":1527780,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T21:21:30.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"8a17e308e5bd9cb64b8443e15c3f34bf540ad192","tid":1527780,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T21:21:50.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"122841ee8d6163e8222c44398349ae2b7aed830a","tid":1527780,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T21:27:27.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"9bd0d766044f4a902c2df514afbe8f0028da68fd","tid":1527780,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T21:50:41.000Z","msg":"唔洗割住<br />\n<br />\n等佢地真係想做大台時 咪打佢地落黎<br />\n攬炒巴一早講左啦"},{"pid":"e011e4040b330353b4e2f22d070c5b3fcc0c542f","tid":1527780,"uid":245484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T21:52:00.000Z","msg":"邊撚個啊你又，由你黎定義?"},{"pid":"6ea8e512e1815001abfdf1f8f76ea522093c6fa2","tid":1527780,"uid":190979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T21:52:31.000Z","msg":"係手足嘅入嚟！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1527346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1527346</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a1955a2cbba0bca29e27d7c3eb8eccaf9fb686d1","tid":1527780,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T22:02:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nwscleungyiuchung/photos/a.677531369054864/1487118888096104/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnwscleungyiuchung%2Fphotos%2Fa.677531369054864%2F1487118888096104%2F&d=I3kI68XCunzd%2BKkpJ1XxGLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=9b3a25e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nwscleungyiuchung/photos/a.677531369054864/1487118888096104/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykF74GT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykF74GT.jpg&h=2c35601f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾巴打自己分析下<br />\n我地唔係藍絲 全部都有獨立思考<br />\n佢地而家有少動作 可能想收割<br />\n我覺得呢個moment呢就未洗割住<br />\n不過就一定要屌柒佢地架啦<br />\n睇佢個濕鳩facebook comment就知咩事啦<br />\n佢地而家呢封信可能都只係想試水溫<br />\n要俾佢地知道 佢地要做大台既話 香港人不能接受<br />\n到佢地準備要SET大台同習大人deal既時候<br />\n記得通知攬炒巴打鳩佢地落黎"},{"pid":"267455d2613aeb12acf8a22a1840e82907bdee9e","tid":1527780,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e011e4040b330353b4e2f22d070c5b3fcc0c542f","tid":1527780,"uid":245484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T21:52:00.000Z","msg":"邊撚個啊你又，由你黎定義?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T22:10:54.000Z","msg":"唔使由邊個去定義的，呢啲係好基本嘅道義，老師無教你？"},{"pid":"9fc40ce3af603077bf443f351414309c9ebd3e04","tid":1527780,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bd0d766044f4a902c2df514afbe8f0028da68fd","tid":1527780,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T21:50:41.000Z","msg":"唔洗割住<br />\n<br />\n等佢地真係想做大台時 咪打佢地落黎<br />\n攬炒巴一早講左啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T22:12:11.000Z","msg":"為時已晚"},{"pid":"88c7805cfdbc7a7a98dab16f32289801e4576104","tid":1527780,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fc40ce3af603077bf443f351414309c9ebd3e04","tid":1527780,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bd0d766044f4a902c2df514afbe8f0028da68fd","tid":1527780,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T21:50:41.000Z","msg":"唔洗割住<br />\n<br />\n等佢